code: // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) {         return false.     }     SlotID slotID = (SlotID) o.     return slotNumber == slotID.slotNumber && resourceId.equals(slotID.resourceId). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     int result = resourceId.hashCode().     result = 31 * result + slotNumber.     return result. }
@Override public String toString() {     return resourceId + "_" + slotNumber. }
